## Settings
borderwidth 0
snapdist 15
gap 10 10 10 10
sticky yes
moveamount 15

## Keybinds

unbind-key	all

bind-key	4S-q		quit
bind-key	4S-r		restart
bind-key	4-space		menu-exec
bind-key  4-p     dmenu_run
bind-key	4-Return	st
bind-key  4-v     "create_or_focus dbeaver"

